Roadmap for elCheapo Grinder

1. Test Rig

Aim
  . design 3d print and test fit
  . 3dprint coupling and test fit
  . design and test stepper control
  . stepper torque requirement analysis
  . speed analysis


2. Fixed Rig Prototype1
Aim
  . design 3d print fixed Rig
  . stepper motor and speed control interface (switch and dial)

3. Add wight monitoring and timer
Aim
  . add weighing scale with display
  . Analyze grind time to yield

